               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the donor and his relatives; name of the protagonist; incipit of miracles in Text I; the word "sälam" in Text II; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
